text: Kaltayevo () is a rural locality (a selo) in Sharipovsky Selsoviet, Kushnarenkovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 576 as of 2010. There are 14 streets. == Geography == It is located 20 km from Kushnarenkovo, 13 km from Sharipovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kushnarenkovsky District
title: Kaltayevo, Kushnarenkovsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
